WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.300
Exposing the magic in AI, Tamkin is revolutionizing communication.

00:00:05.300 --> 00:00:08.800
Imagine a world where everyone can effortlessly communicate,

00:00:08.800 --> 00:00:11.100
no matter their language or hearing ability.

00:00:11.100 --> 00:00:13.300
That's the reality Tamkin is creating.

00:00:13.300 --> 00:00:18.400
Tamkin uses advanced AI to provide real-time sign language translation,

00:00:18.400 --> 00:00:23.800
breaking down barriers for over 500 million people who rely on sign language.

00:00:23.800 --> 00:00:27.400
Every year it translates an astonishing 3 billion words,

00:00:27.500 --> 00:00:31.600
making it the world's largest AI-powered sign language platform.

00:00:31.600 --> 00:00:33.400
But Tamkin is more than just numbers,

00:00:33.400 --> 00:00:37.000
it's about making connections and fostering inclusivity.

00:00:37.000 --> 00:00:39.400
By setting a new standard in accessibility,

00:00:39.400 --> 00:00:43.400
Tamkin is transforming how we communicate on a global scale.

00:00:43.400 --> 00:00:46.100
Join us in celebrating the power of AI

00:00:46.100 --> 00:00:49.600
and the brighter, more inclusive future it brings.

00:00:49.600 --> 00:00:52.300
Because with Tamkin, everyone has a voice.